window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>She’s free from the confines of her father’s control. He’s the man hired to keep her out of trouble.</b></p> <p>For Braden Clark, getting paid to watch over a city girl on vacation seems too good to be true. She’s hot as hell and determined to test her newfound boundaries, something he finds both sexy and arousing.&nbsp;</p> <p>Juliette Collins is eager to play and discover everything else she’s missed in her sheltered life - including the hot, muscular guy that seems to be everywhere she looks.But what happens when she discovers his secret? That he’s been paid to watch over her all along?</p> <p><b>This book was formerly called </b><b><i>Freed</i></b><b>. No changes from original.&nbsp;</b></p>"; 
